task.summary: Added all activities layouts and java files.
Added main menu adapter and asynctask.v
Able to move across all activities.
Created toolbars for all activties and worked on messagesadapter now.
Receiving data and parsing it into messsages/chats is done. Now for sending data.
Added lastmessage/timestamp updates, sending new messages, saving messages, etc.
Sending and receiving messages and chat rooms is now functioning.
Deleting chat works if done carefully, still buggy.
Polished snapping to the last message sent when opening chat, adding people to "users" when registering, etc.
Allowed user to back out of the main menu to their home screen.
Added title to be in the Toolbar for each chat.
